            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CodexMate 0.0.7

- Kept notch mode active on Macs without a hardware notch by rendering a centered fake-notch overlay instead of falling back to the menu bar.
- Adjusted the collapsed pixel sprite to scale down with smaller notch heights so the character no longer clips in compact overlays.
- Fixed hover expansion so the fake notch grows downward without cutting off the top edge of the notch or sprite animation.
]]></description>
